OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774631480
OL,3,CNew trial date set for man accused of
OL,4,CChloe Mitchell's murder
OL,6,FA judge has set a new trial date for a
OL,7,Fman accused of the murder of Chloe
OL,8,FMitchell almost three years ago.
OL,10,FBrandon John Rainey's previous legal
OL,11,Fteam walked away from the case stating
OL,12,Fthat they had been "professionally
OL,13,Fcompromised'' and said the defendant
OL,14,Fhad told them that he no longer wished
OL,15,Fthem to represent him.
OL,17,FA new legal team headed up by Des Fahy
OL,18,FKC, instructed by Phoenix Law, came on
OL,19,Frecord in the case last week.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
