FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774631480
OL,3,CNew trial date set for man accused of
OL,4,CChloe Mitchell's murder
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old Rainey of James
OL,7,FStreet, Ballymena, is currently
OL,8,Fawaiting trial and denies murdering
OL,9,Fthe 21-year-old on June 3, 2023, and
OL,10,Fpreventing the lawful burial of her
OL,11,Fremains.
OL,13,FThe defendant was produced from
OL,14,FMaghaberry Prison again on Friday to
OL,15,Fattend the court proceedings while Ms
OL,16,FMitchell's family and friends sat in
OL,17,Fthe public gallery.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774631480
OL,3,CNew trial date set for man accused of
OL,4,CChloe Mitchell's murder
OL,6,FAt Belfast Crown Court, Mr Fahy told
OL,7,FMadam Justice McBride that given the
OL,8,Ffacilities provided at Laganside Court
OL,9,FComplex they were "not conducive to
OL,10,Fcarrying out a consultation in a case
OL,11,Flike this''.
OL,13,FThe defence KC added: "It requires a
OL,14,Fconsiderable period of time in an
OL,15,Fenvironment in which I am able to deal
OL,16,Fwith the instructions which I receive
OL,17,Fand I do not consider that is
OL,18,Favailable in this court building.
OL,20,F"I have engaged fully in this case in
OL,21,Fthe time I have had since last week.''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774631480
OL,3,CNew trial date set for man accused of
OL,4,CChloe Mitchell's murder
OL,6,FMr Fahy confirmed to the court that he
OL,7,Fhad received papers in the case from
OL,8,Fthe previous solicitors.
OL,10,FHe added that the first available date
OL,11,Fprovided by the Prison Service to
OL,12,Fconsult with his client was next
OL,13,FWednesday, April 1.
OL,15,FProsecution counsel David Russell KC
OL,16,Fsaid that as things stood, he
OL,17,Fsuggested pushing the trial back to
OL,18,Fthe end of April.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774631480
OL,3,CNew trial date set for man accused of
OL,4,CChloe Mitchell's murder
OL,6,FHe said the court could hold a review
OL,7,Fof the case on April 13 which had been
OL,8,Fthe intended trial under Rainey's
OL,9,Fprevious legal team.
OL,11,F"By that stage Mr Fahy will have his
OL,12,Finstructions. I can't see the defence
OL,13,Fbeing in a position to start before
OL,14,FApril 27. That is my suggestion,''
OL,15,Fadded Mr Russell.
OL,17,FMadam Justice McBride confirmed that
OL,18,Fthe trial would commence on Tuesday,
OL,19,FApril 28.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
