FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774631480
OL,3,CNew trial date set for man accused of
OL,4,CChloe Mitchell's murder
OL,6,FShe added that she would review the
OL,7,Fcase on April 13 by which time the
OL,8,Fdefence will have received
OL,9,Finstructions from Rainey following a
OL,10,Fprison consultation.
OL,12,FChloe Mitchell's remains were found
OL,13,Fdays after she went missing.
OL,15,FShe was last seen alive on CCTV in
OL,16,FBallymena town centre in the early
OL,17,Fhours of June 3, 2023 and an extensive
OL,18,Fsearch operation was launched by the
OL,19,FPSNI.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
