PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774631480
OL,3,CNew trial date set for man accused of
OL,4,CChloe Mitchell's murder
OL,6,FDetectives investigating her
OL,7,Fdisappearance later launched a murder
OL,8,Finquiry after human remains were
OL,9,Fdiscovered in the Co Antrim town.
OL,11,FThis led officers to attend a flat in
OL,12,Fthe James Street area of the town
OL,13,Fwhich prompted Rainey's arrest.
